Author: samgyoop
Text: I've been bulimic since I was 15 but didn't accept it till I was about 17 honestly. I'm 19 now and worse than ever but it feels totally different after you finally accept it for what it is. Makes you wanna get better once you acknowledge there's something wrong.

Author: Aleph0-4
Text: Same. I thought I was only bulimic since 2 years ago but looking back, I had started purging bigger meals since I was in my early teens (like 6 or 7 years ago) but I just ignored it because it wasn't frequent.
